git --version
```
It should show something like `git version 2.43.0`

---

## Step 4 — Create `.gitignore` file
Before pushing, create a `.gitignore` file in your project folder to avoid pushing unnecessary files:

Create file `.gitignore` and paste this inside:
```
# Python cache files
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# Model files (large files)
model/model.pkl
model/tfidf.pkl

# Dataset (large file)
data/jobs.csv

# VS Code settings
.vscode/

# Environment
venv/
.env